Node.Notes: Uncertain. Most go with minority of ms in MT and LXX traditions and read: you [are worth] ten thousands like us. Tree assumes: Now ten thousands [are] like us.
Uncertain. Most read: Protect for me the young man Absalom. Tree assumes: Watch out for whoever [is] against the young man Absalom.
The referents of this infinitival clause are uncertain. Tree follows MT and sees the Cushite as the servant of the king and Ahimaaz as your servant whom Joab sent
